survey.music_making: I've been playing drums for over 40 years. Have spent time as a session drummer and had a progressive rock band that did decent-ish numbers, we'd sell about 5-10K copies of each album there in the 90s. Nowadays that'd be pretty good numbers in physical sales. Played all over, some festivals, headlined a couple small festivals.
survey.activities: Driving, working, walking, hanging out, any time I'm not watching TV or something pretty much.
survey.habit_change: They really haven't. I've always been obsessed with music.
